---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="BreederHQ - Professional Breeding Management Software"
  description="Modern, all-in-one software for professional animal breeders. Manage breeding cycles, waitlists, genetics, health testing, and client relationships."
>

  <main>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-gray-50 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <img src="/logo.png" alt="BreederHQ" class="h-24 w-auto mx-auto mb-8" />
          <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-6xl">
            Stop using spreadsheets.<br />
            <span class="text-primary">Start breeding smarter.</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="mt-6 text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            BreederHQ is the all-in-one platform that gives professional breeders
            the tools they need to manage breeding cycles, waitlists, genetics,
            health testing, and client relationships‚Äîall in one place.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-10 flex items-center justify-center gap-x-6">
            <a
              href="/coming-soon"
              class="bg-primary text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold hover:opacity-90"
            >
              Get Early Access
            </a>
            <a
              href="/coming-soon"
              class="text-gray-700 px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold hover:text-primary"
            >
              Learn More ‚Üí
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Trust Signals / Metrics -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">
            Trusted by 1,200+ professional breeders
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
            Managing 15,000+ breeding animals across dogs, cats, horses, goats, rabbits, and sheep
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center p-4">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-2">üêï</div>
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-1">8,200+</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Dogs</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center p-4">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-2">üêà</div>
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-1">3,100+</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Cats</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center p-4">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-2">üê¥</div>
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-1">1,800+</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Horses</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center p-4">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-2">üêê</div>
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-1">1,200+</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Goats</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center p-4">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-2">üêá</div>
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-1">500+</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Rabbits</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center p-4">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-2">üêë</div>
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-1">200+</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Sheep</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Problem Statement -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">
          Breeding is complex. Your tools shouldn't be.
        </h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Scattered Data</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Breeding records in spreadsheets, client info in email, health
              records in filing cabinets‚Äîit's time to centralize everything.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Manual Processes</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Manually tracking breeding cycles, sending updates, matching
              puppies to families‚Äîtasks that should be automated.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Poor Client Experience</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Clients expect professionalism. Give them real-time updates,
              online applications, and transparent communication.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Species Bar -->
    <section class="bg-primary py-12">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <p class="text-center text-white text-lg mb-6">
          Built for breeders of
        </p>
        <div class="flex justify-center gap-8 flex-wrap">
          <a href="/dogs" class="text-white hover:underline text-lg font-medium">Dogs</a>
          <a href="/cats" class="text-white hover:underline text-lg font-medium">Cats</a>
          <a href="/horses" class="text-white hover:underline text-lg font-medium">Horses</a>
          <a href="/goats" class="text-white hover:underline text-lg font-medium">Goats</a>
          <a href="/rabbits" class="text-white hover:underline text-lg font-medium">Rabbits</a>
          <a href="/sheep" class="text-white hover:underline text-lg font-medium">Sheep</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Features Overview -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-white">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">
          Everything you need, nothing you don't
        </h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Animal Profiles</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
              Complete records for every animal‚Äîhealth, genetics, pedigree,
              photos, and breeding history.
            </p>
            <a href="/workflows/breeding-cycles" class="text-primary font-medium">Learn more ‚Üí</a>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Breeding Cycles</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
              Track heat cycles, breedings, pregnancies, and whelping dates
              with automated reminders.
            </p>
            <a href="/workflows/breeding-cycles" class="text-primary font-medium">Learn more ‚Üí</a>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Waitlists & Placement</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
              Manage client applications, match families to animals, and
              communicate through every step.
            </p>
            <a href="/workflows/waitlists-and-placement" class="text-primary font-medium">Learn more ‚Üí</a>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Genetics & Health</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
              Store test results, track genetic lines, and make data-driven
              breeding decisions.
            </p>
            <a href="/workflows/genetics-and-health-testing" class="text-primary font-medium">Learn more ‚Üí</a>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Client Portal</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
              Give clients 24/7 access to updates, photos, documents, and
              their animal's information.
            </p>
            <a href="/workflows/breeding-cycles" class="text-primary font-medium">Learn more ‚Üí</a>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Business Tools</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
              Contracts, deposits, communication templates, and reporting‚Äîall
              the professional tools you need.
            </p>
            <a href="/workflows/breeding-cycles" class="text-primary font-medium">Learn more ‚Üí</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Verification Badge Explanation -->
        <div class="mt-16 bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 rounded-lg p-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Understanding Breeder Verification</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
                When you see a verification badge on a breeder's profile in BreederHQ, it means they've provided
                documentation to prove their breeding program is legitimate. This includes business registration,
                facility information, and references.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
                <strong>Why transparency matters:</strong> Too many buyers get scammed by fake breeders or
                end up with animals from irresponsible sources. Verification helps buyers make informed decisions
                by confirming a breeder is who they say they are.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm italic">
                Note: Verification confirms identity and legitimacy, not breeding practices. Buyers should still
                research health testing, facilities, and breeding ethics independently.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Testimonials Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">
          Trusted by breeders who take their programs seriously
        </h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gray-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold text-gray-600 flex-shrink-0">
                SK
              </div>
              <div class="ml-3">
                <div class="font-semibold">Sarah K.</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Golden Retriever Breeder, Oregon</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 italic">
              "I was losing track of which families were waiting for which litter, and constantly checking
              my spreadsheet for due dates. Now everything is automated and I haven't missed a heat cycle
              reminder in months. My clients love getting photo updates through the portal instead of
              group texts."
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gray-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold text-gray-600 flex-shrink-0">
                MT
              </div>
              <div class="ml-3">
                <div class="font-semibold">Michael T.</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Maine Coon Breeder, Texas</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 italic">
              "I breed three different cat breeds and was drowning in paperwork. Having all my health testing
              results, pedigrees, and breeding plans in one place has saved me hours every week. The genetics
              tracking actually helped me catch a potential issue before I bred two cats that shouldn't be paired."
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gray-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold text-gray-600 flex-shrink-0">
                JR
              </div>
              <div class="ml-3">
                <div class="font-semibold">Jennifer R.</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Quarter Horse Breeder, Kentucky</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 italic">
              "The professionalism factor is huge. I used to send contracts and collect deposits through PayPal
              and email‚Äîit felt sloppy. Now buyers submit applications through my portal, sign contracts digitally,
              and everything is documented. It's made me look like the serious breeder I actually am."
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="bg-primary py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">
          Be Among the First to Experience BreederHQ
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-blue-100 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Join our early adopter program and get exclusive access before our public launch.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/coming-soon"
          class="bg-white text-primary px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold hover:opacity-90 inline-block"
        >
          Request Early Access
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
